    <item>
      <title>亨特通过削减开支和税收来划定选举战线</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/hunt-draws-election-battle-lines-with-cuts-to-spending-and-taxes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国财政大臣杰里米·亨特在为即将到来的选举划定政治战线时，通过窃取工党的旗舰政策和挤压公共服务，向数百万英国工人提供每年 100 亿英镑（127 亿美元）的减税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/hunt-draws-election-battle-lines-with-cuts-to-spending-and-taxes</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 19:35:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>杰里米·亨特延长儿童福利并誓言改革“不公平”制度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/jeremy-hunt-extends-child-benefit-in-budget-and-vows-to-reform-unfair-system</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国财政大臣杰里米·亨特改变了儿童保育福利开始消失的收入门槛后，近 50 万家庭将能够申请儿童保育福利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/jeremy-hunt-extends-child-benefit-in-budget-and-vows-to-reform-unfair-system</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 19:08:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平呼吁“爱国者”加大反台斗争力度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/xi-calls-on-patriots-to-step-up-taiwan-anti-independence-fight</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国家主席习近平在与中国最高调的年度政治聚会相关的一次会议上呼吁动员台湾和海外的“爱国者”，抵御岛上的台独势力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/xi-calls-on-patriots-to-step-up-taiwan-anti-independence-fight</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 19:03:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>海地总理面临下台呼吁，暴力团伙威胁内战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/haiti-violence-gang-leaders-threaten-civil-war-as-pm-faces-call-to-quit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[海地总理阿里尔·亨利正面临辞职或提出新政府计划的压力，因为发动致命暴力的帮派头目加强了对该国的控制并威胁内战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/haiti-violence-gang-leaders-threaten-civil-war-as-pm-faces-call-to-quit</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 18:50:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院定于 4 月 25 日进行特朗普豁免权辩论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/supreme-court-schedules-trump-immunity-argument-for-april-25</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院表示，将于 4 月 25 日听取有关唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 寻求刑事起诉豁免的辩论，该案有可能将他的选举干扰审判推迟到 11 月大选之后。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/supreme-court-schedules-trump-immunity-argument-for-april-25</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 18:49:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登任命波德斯塔为气候外交官受到共和党调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/biden-s-naming-of-podesta-as-top-climate-diplomat-probed-by-gop</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国会共和党人正在调查总统乔·拜登任命约翰·波德斯塔取代约翰·克里作为其首席气候外交官的决定，指责白宫在没有经过参议院确认程序的情况下任命他规避法律。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/biden-s-naming-of-podesta-as-top-climate-diplomat-probed-by-gop</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 18:35:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>民主党人迪恩·菲利普斯结束了对拜登的长期挑战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/democrat-dean-phillips-ends-long-shot-challenge-to-biden</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国众议员迪恩·菲利普斯暂停了他的总统竞选活动，结束了他挑战总统乔·拜登争夺民主党提名的渺茫竞选活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/democrat-dean-phillips-ends-long-shot-challenge-to-biden</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 18:19:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国会将投票决定为会议城市筹集安全资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/congress-to-vote-on-raising-security-funds-for-convention-cities</link>
      <description><![CDATA[芝加哥和密尔沃基是今年夏天民主党和共和党全国代表大会的主办城市，预计将获得总计 1.5 亿美元的联邦资金，用于活动的安保费用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/congress-to-vote-on-raising-security-funds-for-convention-cities</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 18:07:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克表示他不会向任何一位总统候选人捐款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/elon-musk-says-he-won-t-donate-to-either-presidential-candidate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克表示，他不会向可能的共和党候选人唐纳德·特朗普或总统乔·拜登捐款，并在本周早些时候与共和党候选人会面后淡化了预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/elon-musk-says-he-won-t-donate-to-either-presidential-candidate</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 15:31:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃及意外加息，国际货币基金组织释放 80 亿美元贷款以缓解危机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/egypt-gets-breakthrough-imf-deal-to-lift-loan-size-to-8-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃及和国际货币基金组织同意将该国的救助计划增加一倍多，达到 80 亿美元，这是近期全球为稳定因战争和通货膨胀而资金短缺的地区关键国家所做努力的顶峰。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/egypt-gets-breakthrough-imf-deal-to-lift-loan-size-to-8-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 14:29:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
